snippet.title: Midnight Witch Trailer
snippet.description:
Free download (Steam): https://store.steampowered.com/app/2336180/Midnight_Witch/
Free download (itch.io): https://bren-mw.itch.io/midnight-witch

Trapped in a rigged game by a mysterious Witch. Do you have what it takes to solve the riddle and save the one you love… or can you even make it out alive?

Created by Bren MW: https://twitter.com/Bren_MW
